_sText:
This is a map I just randomly made in hammer. I did not use any pens or paper. Just randomly made a room with some corridors and a bridge thing ect..
It took me around 4 hours to make. Every single texture you cant see is nodraw so there is no lag.
It is a smallish size but can hold up to around 40 people at the total max. I got the idea from one of my last maps (gg_lab_test) It turned out to be too small so I made this. A much bigger version. 

Sorry for low quality screen shots. 
Please assess and leave constructive feed back.

Thank you for looking.
